    <!--
        Representative seed catalog — 29 SKUs covering all 9 hardware
        categories (hinge, slide, pin, screw, handle, leveler, cam_lock,
        bumper, other). The 179-row Marathon workbook import replaces
        this file when the trade-account session lands.

        Every SKU has x_pricing_pending=True because trade-account login
        is needed to resolve cost/price.

        Vendor info (product.supplierinfo) links each SKU to Marathon —
        the configurator-resolution method picks SKUs by x_marathon_sku,
        which is the stable identifier inside hardware_map.json.

        2026-06-10 audit — added 15 SKUs covering the Marathon category
        gaps that surfaced during brand audit (DTC hinges, King Slide
        slides, more pull sizes/finishes, hinge accessories). Part
        numbers follow Marathon's documented naming convention but
        are NOT verified against the live catalog — Path B (catalog
        file ingest) replaces them with authoritative SKUs.
    -->

